\f0\b\fs20 \cf0 Assess your facebook mobile risks
\f1\b0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl240\sa312

\f0\fs20 \cf0 Like Twitter, Facebook is a way to get your messages to a potentially large audience. It is not a secure method of communication for sensitive information.
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs20 This article offers advice about how to mitigate risks when using Facebook as a dissemination and organizing tool. In particular, we consider the following risks:
\f1\fs24 \
